{"tid":1609242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學生同我入嚟 十月二 罷佢老母","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:55.000Z","uid":210461,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2afd262bd5fbfd9654a59480db7cd8bcdafa1c2f","tid":1609242,"uid":210461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"今日有中五同學仔俾狗用實彈射擊 係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">謀殺</span></strong></span>事件 大家聽日唔係仲可以正常返學呀？ <br />\n你可能唔夠膽上前線 但你做到嘅野仲有好多 <br />\n人哋出去擋子彈 你哋都應該會出返分力<br />\n我地要話比中槍同被捕手足知<br />\nYou are not alone<br />\n佢哋唔係condom<br />\n馬都唔可以照跑啦<br />\n可能大家覺罷課效益唔大 但唔代表唔做<br />\n而家社會出現極權情況<br />\n我地中學生等於未來棟樑 要改變呢個社會 要清楚而家社會發生咩狀況<br />\n當手足仲瞓緊係醫院 隨時俾人告暴動罪 要坐成十碌 大家絕對唔可以安然冇事咁上堂聽書<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊罷佢老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月二 全民起義！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"09e5738f0e6b897f383d23991663a4a1a877b348","tid":1609242,"uid":210461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"自推十下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c296ea609d82ec9758dd901b81d611b8ed711ea","tid":1609242,"uid":210461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:04:33.000Z","msg":"中槍手足要頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4edbd98747f41b5797ac4666259330206a91baf","tid":1609242,"uid":210461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"學生罷課要人！"},{"pid":"2a9e19209bb3633372b633959762af0f17e8fa2d","tid":1609242,"uid":210461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:06:28.000Z"